  2 |  * Context Slice Manager - Smart Context Management for FreeAgent Cockpit
  3 |  * 
  4 |  * Creates modular "slices" of context that can be loaded/unloaded dynamically
  5 |  * to optimize token usage while maintaining conversation context.
  6 |  * 
  7 |  * Features:
  8 |  * - Modular context slices (session, project, task, system, memory)
  9 |  * - Dynamic loading/unloading of context slices
 10 |  * - Configurable max context tokens (default: 100k for Claude, 32k for Gemini)
 11 |  * - LRU eviction when context exceeds limits
 12 |  * - Integration with iteration governor for safety
 13 |  * 
 14 |  * Methods:
 15 |  * - createSlice(): Create a new context slice
 16 |  * - loadSlice(): Load a slice into active context
 17 |  * - unloadSlice(): Unload a slice from active context
 18 |  * - getActiveSlices(): Get all currently active slices
 19 |  * - optimizeContext(): Optimize context to fit within token limits
 20 |  * - getContextSummary(): Get summary of all slices and their states
